name: virginia emissions testing locations
description: This alphabetical by city listing includes facilities in Northern Virginia that have been permitted to operate as vehicle emissions inspection stations under the Air Check Virginia vehicle emissions inspection program. DEQ recommends calling ahead to see if the facility you've chosen is currently active or to obtain other information such as inspection hours or available emissions repair services.
